version_description: Easy to play, and good for most voices. It's not the original key of A, but this is better for a novice.
Complete with Intro and Coda / thoroughly ear-transcribed / intermediate with transitional chords (sus4 and split chords) / 2 versions in different keys / suggestions for special voicings.
Arranged to play as a reggae tune using minor and minor 7th chords.
